!--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
! Build Material & Construction definitions for envelope 
!    floor on fill, ext walls, roof/ceilings, ext doors (opaque), 
!    ext windows/glass doors, party walls)
!--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

! FLOOR-ON-Fill

Material,
